 P2     J2     J3      300.0   100.0     100.0      0.0        Open
 P3     J3     T1      200.0   100.0     100.0      0.5        Open
 P4     J1     J3      800.0    80.0     100.0      0.0        Closed

[PUMPS]
;ID     Node1  Node2   Parameters
 PU1    R1     J1      HEAD HC1

[VALVES]
